# Closed-loop staging artifacts are transient; never commit them. The labeled
# store (data/training_data/labeled.jsonl) and autotrain report ARE tracked so
# they persist across stateless cloud runs.
data/training_data/staging/

# X/Twitter sentiment module: the signal history must persist across stateless
# cloud runs, so un-ignore it from the global *.parquet rule above.
!data/history/twitter_llm_signal.parquet
